title: Dale - Riot In English - 9-25599-2 - PRNArchive - PRN Archive
description:
Dale Bozzio's one and only album on Prince's Paisley Park Records.


Includes the Prince composition "Simon Simon."


********


If you want to share more Prince (and associated artists) CDs in lossless quality, tag your uploads with PRNArchive.


Rips should be created with Exact Audio Copy, as one continuous audio image, with accompanying CUE file and LOG file. The audio image can either be uploaded as an uncompressed WAV, or compressed with FLAC.


If you want to include a separate folder of MP3 files, or scans, you are more than welcome - but the important contents are the continuous lossless WAV (or FLAC), CUE file, and EAC LOG file.


PRNArchive / PRN Archive




********


If you would like to separate the continuous audio image file, use the freeware program Medieval Cue Splitter, to split the continuous file into separate tracks.
